thread.title: Toxic gases from Indonesian volcano send 30 to hospital

title: Toxic gases from Indonesian volcano send 30 to hospital
text:
Toxic gases from Indonesian volcano send 30 to hospital Thursday, March 22, 2018 - 00:43 
Thick clouds of sulfurous gas billow from Mount Ijen in Indonesia, sending 30 people to hospital and prompting the closure of the popular tourist destination. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
